                    <p>Compare the products and services on offer and take advantage of some  amazing show only specials. </p>
                    <p>Keep an eye out on this website, subscribe to our newsletter and like us on Facebook to receive all up-to-date expo information for your visit.﻿</p>
                </div>                
            </div>
        </section>

